org.apache.flink.runtime.rest.handler.legacy.metrics

类 MetricFetcher<T extends RestfulGateway>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.rest.handler.legacy.metrics.MetricFetcher<T>

  • public class MetricFetcher<T extends RestfulGateway>
extends java.lang.Object
    The MetricFetcher can be used to fetch metrics from the JobManager and all registered TaskManagers.

    Metrics will only be fetched when update() is called, provided that a sufficient time since the last call has passed.
